Package careerhub.storage

Class InMemoryApplicationRepository

java.lang.Object
careerhub.storage.InMemoryApplicationRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
ApplicationRepository
public class InMemoryApplicationRepository extends Object implements ApplicationRepository
In-memory implementation of ApplicationRepository.

This repository stores all Application objects inside a HashMap, using IDs such as A1, A2, A3... which auto-increment. It is used by the system as the main runtime storage and also supports syncing the ID counter when loading from CSV (where IDs already exist).

This class contains no business logic; it is purely data storage.
